From: Sam James <sam@gentoo.org>
Subject: [PATCH] Enable CET (-fcf-protection=full) by default

Needs:
- CET to be enabled for GCC
- -DEXTRA_OPTIONS_CF to be passed during build (via toolchain.eclass).

Only supported on amd64.
